### 2. `doctor_schedule` — Jadwal Operasional Per Poli

> Menggantikan 3 kartu jadwal hardcoded di `app/page.tsx` (baris 443–536). Juga menjadi **source of truth** untuk logika `checkStatusKlinik()`.

```sql
CREATE TABLE doctor_schedule (
  id              UUID    PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  service_id      UUID    NOT NULL REFERENCES services(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  hari_mulai      SMALLINT NOT NULL,    -- 1=Senin, 6=Sabtu (ISO weekday)
  hari_selesai    SMALLINT NOT NULL,    -- 1=Senin, 6=Sabtu
  jam_buka_pagi   TIME    NOT NULL,     -- '08:00:00'
  jam_tutup_pagi  TIME    NOT NULL,     -- '12:00:00'
  jam_buka_sore   TIME,                 -- '14:00:00' (NULL = tidak ada sesi sore)
  jam_tutup_sore  TIME,                 -- '18:00:00'
  catatan         TEXT,
  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),

  CONSTRAINT valid_hari CHECK (hari_mulai >= 1 AND hari_selesai <= 6 AND hari_mulai <= hari_selesai),
  CONSTRAINT valid_jam_pagi CHECK (jam_buka_pagi < jam_tutup_pagi)
);
```

**Seed Data Awal (berdasarkan jadwal yang ada di halaman):**

| Poli | Hari | Pagi | Sore |
|---|---|---|---|
| Poli Umum | Senin–Jumat | 08:00–12:00 | 14:00–18:00 |
| Poli Umum | Sabtu | 08:00–12:00 | 16:00–18:00 |
| Poli Gigi | Senin–Jumat | 08:00–12:00 | 14:00–18:00 |
| Poli Gigi | Sabtu | 08:00–12:00 | 16:00–18:00 |
| Poli KIA | Senin–Jumat | 08:00–12:00 | 14:00–18:00 |
| Poli KIA | Sabtu | 08:00–12:00 | 16:00–18:00 |

